<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmattri<unclear>bhuvanacakravartti</unclear> śrī<unclear>rājarājadēvara</unclear> vijayarājya saṁvatsaramulu 4 gu śrāhi śakavarṣaṁbulu 1072 ṇḍagunēṇṭi Ā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṣāḍa śuddha Aṣṭamiyu nādivāramunāṁḍu svasti caraṇasarōru<unclear>ha</unclear>vihatavilōcanatrilōcanapramukhākhilapridhvīśvarakāritakāvērītīrakā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rikālakularatnapradīpāhitakumārāṁkuśa śrīmanmahā<unclear>ma</unclear>ṁḍalēśvara tribhuvanamalladēvacōḍamahārājula mūlabhrityu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁḍaina ceṁjeṟvula saudamu Eṟiyamanāyakuni koḍku ga <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bairavanāyakuṁḍu kammanāṁṭi prēṁpalli śrībhāvanārāyaṇadē 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>varaku Uttarāyaṇasaṁkrāṁtti nimittamuna Ācaṁdrārkka <unclear>ma</unclear>khaṁḍavartti dīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina velleḍlu 50 vīniṁ jēkoni Erṛcūri
<lb n="6"/>kāṭiya<note n="81-1">The letter ya is cut below the line in the original.</note>bōyuṁḍuṁ dana putrānupavitrikamu nitya mā<unclear>ne</unclear>ṁḍu neyu vōyaṁggalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti va
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>suṁdharā</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> ṣaṣṭi<unclear>rvarṣa</unclear>sahāsrāṇi viṣṭāyā <unclear>jāyatē kri</unclear>mi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
